time complexity: O(n) for get, addAtIndex, deleteAtIndex; O(1) for addAtHead, addAtTail
space complexity: O(n)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: Uses a singly-linked list with a size counter for O(1) bounds checking. Traversals are minimal due to small constraint (≤2000 calls).

